When deploying both Confluence and Jira users are now experiencing an OutOfMemory error concerning the PermGen space

{code}
java.lang.OutOfMemoryError: PermGen space
{code}

As a work around you will need to add the following parameter on startup
{code}
-XX:MaxPermSize=128m
{code}

