The roadmap is a valuable tool for us to keep track of issues.  Typically we have different teams owning and testing Jiras from those who are fixing them.  What would be nice would be to easily distinguish between open Jiras and closed Jiras.  It's easy to see the difference between jiras that have been resolved and those that haven't but you only have a small icon on the right to see which ones are open.  It's hard to see at a glance how many jiras have yet to be tested which paints a better picture of the road map particualarly if many issues have been resolved but none have been tested yet.

